item.title: CVE-2020-2126|2024-08-04T07:01:40.785Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20digitalocean%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins DigitalOcean Plugin 1.1 and earlier stores a token unencrypted in the global config.xml file on the Jenkins master where it can be viewed by users with access to the master file system.
